	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Wow... I just wanted to mention I downloaded Notepad++... I think life will be a lot easier now! I see why lots of people use it. At first I wasn't sure that it would be useful as I wasn't sure it would recognize 6502. But with the customization features available, I was able to make it recognize all the 6502 instructions, and highlight them all blue. Then comments are green, things like ".incbin" and ".include" are red... All the lines are numbered... I certainly hope there's more than 1 undo, which is something about Notepad that drove me nuts. I'm just relieved to not have to open my code and have to look at a sea indistinguishable black terminal characters. So yeah, I'd recommend downloading it if you haven't already.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


